Buddy Roosevelt https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Buddy_Roosevelt 0 Buddy Roosevelt (June 25, 1898 — October 6, 1973) was an American film and television actor and stunt performer from Hollywood's early silent film years through the 1950s.
